                <h1>Faculty reflect on Brodhead&#039;s tenure, praise leadership and global outreach efforts</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/2fbd9f5c-999e-41a7-86c7-f474190eac1d.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="The&#x20;Devils&#x20;took&#x20;down&#x20;the&#x20;Florida&#x20;State&#x20;Seminoles,&#x20;previously&#x20;undefeated&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;ACC,&#x20;Saturday&#x20;at&#x20;Indoor&#x20;Cameron&#x20;Stadium" class="w-100">
